## Input

```css
%toolbelt {
  border: 1px solid black;
}

.message {
  color: red;
}

.action-buttons {
  @extend %toolbelt !optional;
}

.alert {
  @extend .message;
  @extend .message, .info;
  @extend a:hover;
}

@extend .message;

@extend .icon-#{$name};

@include themed-button {
  @extend .message;
}

```


